@startuml
!include ../../style.puml

'[common]
actor Alice
box "Cluster" #E6F3FF
participant athens
participant byzantium
participant cyrene
end box
'[/common]

' [step1 {"name":"Run 1"}]
== Run 1 ==
Alice -> athens : set("title", "After Dawn")
athens -> byzantium : replicate write
byzantium -[#blue]-> athens : ack arrives early
athens -[#red]>x cyrene : message lost
note over cyrene #FFCCBC
Cyrene crashed or isolated
before receiving the message
end note
athens --> Alice : success
' [/step1]

' [step2 {"name":"Run 2", "newPage":"true"}]
== Run 2 ==
Alice -> athens : set("title", "After Dawn")
athens -> byzantium : replicate write
athens ->x cyrene : message lost
... ack delayed ...
byzantium -[#blue]-> athens : ack arrives later 
athens -[#red]>x athens : timeout / retry path differs
note over cyrene #FFCCBC
Cyrene crashed or isolated 
before receiving the message
end note
' [/step2]

note over athens,cyrene #FFF2CC
Same injected fault and same write can still lead to a different execution trace
because internal timing changes when acknowledgements become visible.
end note

@enduml
